data.description: BRING ALL OFFERS!!!!! Seller is very motivated. Welcome to this beautiful home in Grey Oaks Estates. The main floor features a formal dining room with coffered ceilings and wainscoting, a formal living room, a great room with coffered ceilings, an in-law suite with bathroom and an open kitchen with gas range, double ovens, walk-in pantry and granite countertops. On the second floor you will find four more bedrooms, all with vaulted ceiling, a large media room, the laundry room and an amazing master suite that hosts a walk-in closet that is bigger than some bedrooms. Outside you will enjoy your evenings with landscape lighting under the beautiful covered porch looking out at your large yard. The shed is big enough to keep a riding lawn mower and all of your landscaping tools. Come and see your dream home today.
